      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s basically brand new and has been pampered since day one\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, mint condition and drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and kept up with every little detail. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
