    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is absolute: the VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The limited-slip differential and suspension geometry remain tight, offering the sharp turn-in and telepathic feedback these chassis are known for. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this is a turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
