      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute masterpiece of preservation, looking and driving exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips, scratches, or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats remain supple and free of any wear or creasing, and the original protective films are still present on several interior components. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been strictly serviced at authorized dealerships with a full documented history included. With exceptionally low mileage and always kept in a climate-controlled garage, this car represents the pinnacle of its model. It is truly a turn-key collector\u2019s item for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
