    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-parked and spotless. No scratches, no dings, and the interior still has that fresh feel. It\u2019s a total dream to drive! If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in top-notch shape, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
