    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen is in concours-level condition, retaining its factory-original paint depth and structural carbon fiber roof integrity. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative; proactive maintenance includes VAC-treated rod bearings and ARP hardware to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly reliability. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission executes lightning-fast gear synchronization, paired with a perfectly functioning GKN variable M-differential. The suspension geometry remains precise, with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing immediate valving response across all modes. Zero deferred maintenance, no subframe fatigue, and a documented service history make this one of the finest examples remaining for the serious driver.",
